reviewText: A Christmastime favorite! Its definitely not Christmas without this movie. I wish I could find it on dvd!
I purchased this when my oldest was young now I purchased it for her kid
I watch this every Christmas and i'm 22.

I bought this VHS because my 20 year old daughter and I watched this video so much when she was a child that the vhs finally broke. She loved it so much I was looking for it so we could re-watch the famous video of her childhood. It's a vhs tape so it has some bad places in it, but all in all, it was a good vhs tape for the money.
